# Graphify scan excludes — keeps the knowledge graph CODE-ONLY, so it builds
# fully locally (tree-sitter AST) with no LLM backend / API key / data egress.
#
# NOTE: when this file exists, graphify uses it INSTEAD of .gitignore for this
# directory, so the build/dependency excludes below are repeated from .gitignore
# on purpose (otherwise node_modules etc. would be scanned).

# build output & dependencies
node_modules/
.next/
out/
build/
coverage/
.git/
graphify-out/
.vercel/
.superpowers/
*.tsbuildinfo

# docs, prose & images — excluded so the corpus needs no semantic (LLM) pass.
# Mirrors graphify's DOC_EXTENSIONS (.md .mdx .qmd .txt .rst .html .yaml .yml).
*.md
*.mdx
*.qmd
*.txt
*.rst
*.html
*.yaml
*.yml
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.gif
*.svg
*.webp
*.ico
*.pdf
